 <title>SDS and  Customer Recovery Journey</title>
 <link>https://pilotlight.iriss.org.uk/resources/sds-and-customer-recovery-journey</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-resource-who field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Who is it for?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;The SDS and Customer Recovery Journey is for other Alcohol and Drugs Partnerships embarking on SDS implementation.&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;What does it do?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;The SDS and Customer Recovery Journey illustrates how SDS could fit within the Aberdeenshire Alcohol and Drugs Partnership Customer Recovery Journey.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-resource-how field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;How can you use it?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;The SDS and Customer Recovery Journey is designed to illustrate where SDS fits within the recovery journey. It also illustrated where SDS peer workers can provide information and support to individuals in recovery.&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
